{
  "texts": [
    "This guarantees that the token limit will not be exceeded.",
    "In early experiments.",
    "we found that the children's labels alone were not enough to generate a meaningful label for the parent cluster.",
    "To improve, we insert the document summaries randomly sampled from the cluster.",
    "We enforce that each child has at least one article being sampled, and distribute the remaining token space proportionally to the size of each child."
  ]
}